{"tid":1817191,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"去年首十一月有逾3.6萬人持單程證來港。","createTime":"2020-01-09T01:06:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T10:43:29.000Z","uid":267488,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"67fd16c6707f74e7cbc95549774572428ef6baae","tid":1817191,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T01:06:32.000Z","msg":"保安局表示，去年一月至十一月有逾3.6萬人持單程證來港。 <br />\n<br />\n保安局局長李家超書面回覆議員查詢時指，去年一月至十一月有36527人持單程證來港，當中25至44歲佔四成二，約有1.5萬人。<br />\n<br />\n另外，非本地居民亦可透過「受養人政策」來港，去年一至十一月申請受養人簽證的宗數，有近3.4萬宗，創五年新高，有逾2.3萬宗個案獲批，三千二百人被拒。<br />\n<br />\n「受養人政策」是讓原本已獲准來港就業就讀或優才計劃等人士，申請其配偶、子女及父母來港。<br />\n<br />\n又3.6萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd4155505d0e37fb63c8c5fa27c4ded42ae1214","tid":1817191,"uid":301511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T01:08:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6939a211e6671d3c9aba22a98ac4d5bcf0c9113d","tid":1817191,"uid":53498,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T01:09:36.000Z","msg":"屌你老母咪撚再搵支那女人得唔得,娶一個都算仆你個街帶成個家族嚟香港,無錢就食資源,有錢就呃資源"},{"pid":"91f7060dbf63758236fe8ae9419ac8496c8d4e19","tid":1817191,"uid":258598,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T01:11:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81dc3878517c726ed96606336cacaefa09371b2a","tid":1817191,"uid":53498,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"91f7060dbf63758236fe8ae9419ac8496c8d4e19","tid":1817191,"uid":258598,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"6939a211e6671d3c9aba22a98ac4d5bcf0c9113d","tid":1817191,"uid":53498,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T01:09:36.000Z","msg":"屌你老母咪撚再搵支那女人得唔得,娶一個都算仆你個街帶成個